It's cool but have a lot of things to improve, I think for a paid game that's not ok...
- The player loose the ball while running with the ball;
- You put your target to pass, and the ball go to other direction;
- A lot of delay in some actions, like, I run with the ball I dribble, and after dribble the opponnent I lost the ball 1 meter away;
- The passes direction is bad, receiving the ball is bad too, c'mon, If the ball comes to me, why the player left the ball passing him?
JOGO DE PISSA!!! MESMO PASSANDO ALGUM TEMPO, VOLTEI, A MERDA SÓ CHEIRA AINDA PIOR, QUE NOJO DE JOGO, DELAY DEVIA SER O NOME DESTE LIXO!

The game have potential, but need to improve a lot
UNTIL NOW? LOST MONEY

PROS

- It's fun especially if you have friends;
- It's a unique game never seen before;

CONS

- Full of bugs;
- Useless fixes that dont fix nothing;
- Constant crashes;
- Laggy servers;
- Gameplay doesn't feel smooth compared to betas;
- Certain mechanics don't work like dribbling, tackling and the goalkeeper feels weaker in range and defense;
- Unfair matchmaking probably non-existent especially in Ranked mode;
- Priorities doesn't work you as a goalkeeper you catch the ball and they still score then on replay shows that you didn't catch the ball but on your screen you indeed catch it;
- You intercept an enemy player and still they keep the ball;

It's far from been a good game they are prioritizing cosmetics and mechanics over fixing the actual game because this is trash horrible worse that ever been, even in betas this game was 100% better that his full release, it should have been delayed for better gameplay quality and servers definitely, I recommend the game if you like football. Will I be able to give a positive review absolutely not, not while the game is in this sorry state
